sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Client
  participant G as Gateway
  participant U as user-service
  participant S as any service

  C->>G: POST /api/auth/login
  G->>U: (public path) login
  U-->>C: 200 { JWT(sub=email, userId) }

  Note over C,S: later, an authenticated request

  C->>G: GET /api/tasks (Bearer JWT, spoofed X-User-Id: 1)
  G->>G: strip client X-User-* headers
  G->>G: validate JWT (HS256)
  G->>S: GET /api/tasks (X-User-Id: 64, X-User-Role: USER)
  S->>S: read identity from trusted header
  S-->>C: 200 (scoped to the real user)
